title: Change (Taylor's Version)
description:
Taylor didn't need to make any changes to this song.. The lyrics just hit differently now!
She wrote this song to honor someone and now, the same lyrics apply while she is taking back the power by re-releasing her albums.
Find out what Change is all about while Ana, Lacey and Nick break this song down!
